   <center>     <h3>               TABLE OF CONTENTS    </h3>  </center>


<a href="preface.html">PREFACE  </a> <p>     
                                      
<a href="aboutcei.html"> ABOUT THE CENTER FOR ENVIRONMENTAL 
INFORMATION   </a> <p>    
<a href="steercom.html">CONFERENCE STEERING COMMITTEE                        
  <a/> <p>

<a href="cospons.html">CONFERENCE COSPONSORS     </a>           
<p>
<br>

<b>SESSION I.  THE CLIMATE CHANGE PHENOMENON AND 
SUSTAINABILITY </b>  <p>
<ul>
<li><a href="bolin.html">"IPCC Assessment - An Overview"</a>     <br>
<b>Bert Bolin</b>, Chairman, Intergovernmental Panel 
on Climate
     Change  <p>

