<HTML>
<head><title>U.S. Country Studies Program</title></head>
<body>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="map.gif">
<IMG SRC="csptitle.gif"></CENTER>
<H4><P> Under the U.S. Country Studies Program, the U.S.
Government provides technical and financial support to
developing countries and countries with economies in transition
to help them conduct climate change studies and prepare national
climate change action plans.  These studies will assist countries
in fulfilling requirements under the United Nations Framework
Convention on Climate Change<A
HREF="http://www.ciesin.org/datasets/unced/unced.html">
(UNFCCC)</A>. 
A total of <A HREF="country.html">fifty-five countries</A> on five
continents currently participate in the program.<BR>
<P>
<P>
</H4>
<HR>
<H2><A NAME="webpage.html"> Table of Contents </A></H2>
<H3><IMG SRC="globedot.gif">     <A HREF="climat-l.html">**New**
Climate Network Electronic Conference!!</A></H3>
<H4>The U.S. CSP has established an electronic conference to
provide a forum for developing countries and countries with
economies in transition to discuss hot topics in climate change
studies, national climate change action plans and communications,
and other related issues. Developing and transition countries
only need e-mail access in order to participate! <BR>
<P>
<H3><IMG SRC="globedot.gif">     <A HREF="ap.html">About
the Program</A></H3>
<H4><UL><LI><I><A HREF="ap.html#description">Description and
Objectives</A></I>
<I><LI><A HREF="ap.html#nextphse">Next Phase</A>: Support for National
Action Plans (SNAP)</UL></H5>
<P>
<H3><IMG SRC="globedot.gif">     <A
HREF="country.html">Participating
Countries</A>
<P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="globedot.gif">     <A
HREF="workshop.html">Workshops</A>
<H4><I><UL><LI><A HREF="workshop.html#upcoming">Upcoming Workshops</A>
<LI><A HREF="workshop.html#proceed">Workshop Proceedings and
Summaries</A></I></H4></UL>
<P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="globedot.gif">     <A
HREF="resource.html">Information Resources</A><BR>
<H4><UL><LI><A
