              	<BR>     703.306.1527 (voice) 	<BR>      
jfein@nsf.gov
<P>
<LI><i>Earth System History (ESH)</i> supports coordinated projects 
that
focus on  the past behavior of the coupled Earth-ocean-atmosphere-biosphere
system  conducted to provide insight into the factors that govern 
environmental
 variability, rates of climate change, and large-scale responses to climate
 forcing. 	<BR><STRONG>Contacts:</STRONG> <BR>Herman 
Zimmerman/Division of Atmospheric
