<LI><i>Ecological Rates of Change (EROC)</i> research is supported 
for
projects
 studying the effects of both natural and human-induced changes on 
ecological
 processes, specifically how human-induced global change affects ecological
 rates of change. 	<BR><STRONG>Contact: <BR></STRONG>Scott 
Collins/Division 
