<P>
<LI><i>Environmental Technology</i> research support is provided 
to assess
any  environmental technology (including hardware and software), system,
or  service -- the primary purpose of which is to reduce residual 
risk
or cost,  and/or to improve process efficiency. This research area includes
avoidance  of environmental harm, pollution prevention, control, 
monitoring
and  assessment, and restoration.<BR> 	<STRONG>Contacts: 
