<LI><i>Global Tropospheric Chemistry Program (GTCP)</i> supports 
research that  
measures, analyzes, and predicts changes in the 
chemistry
of the global  atmosphere, with emphasis placed on changes affecting the
radiative  processes and oxidizing capacity of the atmosphere and the 
atmospheric
 components of biogeochemical cycles. 
