<LI><i>Greenhouse Gas Dynamics (GGD)</i> research is conducted to 
analyze
 interactions of greenhouse gases with light, other atmospheric gases, 
surfaces,
 and other relevant substances and the complex natural and industrial  
processes
that lead to greenhouse gas production and release.
