<LI><i>Water and Energy: Atmosphere, Vegetative, and Earth Interactions
 (WEAVE)</i> research is supported to gain better understanding of 
energy
and
 water in climate processes and to clarify how the atmosphere, surface
 hydrologic, and biotic processes maintain the global energy balance and
