http://gcrio.org:80/USGCRP/sustain/preface.html 198.76.82.10 19970101083835 text/html 3706
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 08:38:24 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Last-modified: Mon, 21 Oct 1996 18:50:44 GMT
