<DOCNO>WT12-B36-102</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000016-B001-194</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://gcrio.org:80/USGCRP/sustain/michaels.html 198.76.82.10 19970101092308 text/html 16122
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 09:22:59 GMT
