<body>
<h1>THE CLIMATE CHANGE ACTION PLAN</h1><hr><p>

<h2>President William J. Clinton</h2>
<h2>Vice President Albert Gore, Jr.</h2>

<h3>October, 1993</h3>

<blockquote>
With respect to information received about such projects under section 1605, the Department of Energy will coordinate with the Environmental Protection Agency to enable it to fulfill its responsibilities under the Global Climate Protection Act of 1987 and the Clean Air Act, as amended.<p>
</blockquote>


