Associated With Predicting Significant Changes In Seasonal To Interannual 
Variability?</a></ol><p>
<li><a href="hiliteb.html">Climate Change Over The Next Few Decades</a><p>
<ol><li><a href="hiliteb1.html">What New Evidence Is There About Processes 
That Result In Changes In Greenhouse Gases And Aerosol Concentrations In The 
Atmosphere?</a><p>
<li><a href="hiliteb2.html">What Has Been Learned About The Influence Of 
Clouds And Other Feedbacks On Climate?</a><p>
<li><a href="hiliteb3.html">What Has Been Learned About The Influences Of 
Ecosystem Changes On Climate?</a><p>
<li><a href="hiliteb4.html">What Has Been Learned About Future Climate Changes 
From Research On Past Climate Changes Over The History Of The Earth?</a><p>
<li><a href="hiliteb5.html">What Improvements Have Been Made In Predicting 
Future Changes In Climate?</a><p>
<li><a href="hiliteb6.html">What New Evidence Is There That The Climate Is 
Changing In Response To Societal Activities?</a><p>
<li><a href="hiliteb7.html">What Has Been Learned About The Potential 
Consequences Of Climate Change?</a><p>
<li><a href="hiliteb8.html">What New Information Is There Regarding The 
Potential For Society To Adapt To And Mitigate Climate Change?
</a></ol><p>
