<H3><A NAME="proceed"><B>Workshop Proceedings and Other
Publications</B></A></H3>
<H5>The U.S. CSP is collaborating with countries to prepare
conference proceedings to present the comprehensive results of
the climate change country studies, summarizing the results from
all aspects of the studies. Policy summaries of past workshops
are also available. The U.S. CSP has also collaborated with other
countries to produce guidance documents and synthesis reports.  
<H4><B>Workshop Proceedings*</B></H4>
<H6><UL><LI><P>Bonduki Y, Bowers L, Braatz B, Pereira N,
